Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper deals with image processing and noise reduction, which are core topics in computer vision. 
2. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with color images, which are a common type of multimedia data. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses deep learning algorithms for noise reduction, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper proposes a novel deep neural network architecture for identifying impulses in images. 
5. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper uses information theory concepts such as entropy and mutual information to evaluate the performance of the proposed method.
